</definition>
<definition id="fs-idp18119840">
<term>Scopes Monkey Trial</term> <meaning id="fs-idp15322832">the 1925 trial of John Scopes for teaching evolution in a public school; the trial highlighted the conflict between rural traditionalists and modern urbanites</meaning>
</definition>
